ance of any content supplied by the computed shape"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"source."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSource"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlncomputedshapesourcedatasource","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Data source for "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSource"},{"type":"text","text":". This protocol defines two optional methods for fetching"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"data, one based on tile coordinates, and one based on a bounding box. Classes that implement this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"protocol must implement one, and only one of the methods. Methods on this protocol will not be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"called on main thread, they will be called on the caller’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"requestQueue"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource"}],"title":"MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource","kind":"symbol"}}}